Package com.alex323glo.spacex.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AccessRestrictionException
    Exception, which is thrown, when system tries to give access to client as non-existed in system's DB User.
    AppException
    General Exception type for SpaceX application.
    ArgumentValidationException
    Exception, which is thrown, when entered arguments can't pass validation.
    DAOException
    Exception. which is thrown, when system tries to access DB using some DAO.
    DaoRecordNotFoundException
    Exception, which is thrown, when system tries to find a record in DB.
    DaoRecordOverrideException
    Exception, which is thrown, when system tries to write new record to DB.
    EmailDuplicationException
    Exception, which is thrown, when system tries to register user with email, which is currently exists in system's Data Base.
    EmailNotExistsException
    Exception, which is thrown when system tries to access User data in system's DB by non-existing email.
    FilePathException
    Exception, which is thrown, when file path doesn't fit some requirements or templates, which are strongly required.
    LoadFileException
    Exception, which is thrown, when system has problems with load of needed file from system's resources.
    TokenNotExistsException
    Exception, which i thrown, when system tries to use not existing token.
